# Targets_vilhelmsborg_community

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of Targets_vilhelmsborg_community is to generate potential species pools, Phylogenetic diversity maps, Richness maps, and Rarity maps for the Vilhemsborg area, based on a national code found in this [repo](https://github.com/derek-corcoran-barrios/Targets_Species_Community/tree/master).
